msContents.summary: A work on ethics, divided into four books, that closely follows the work of Aristotle. Dedicated to Ippolito d'Este, cardinal of Ferrara.
msContents.textLang: Italian, with a few words in Greek

msItem.title: Divisione e dichiaratione de le virtu morali, f. 59r
La forteza et de suoi estremi, f. 155r
La giustitia et ingiustitia universale, f. 271r

supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 317; [1-317]; modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by a single hand.
